title: Make Hyde Square Your New Home
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 9', 'OR Text', '9', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 634-677 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Hyde Square represents a new generation of modern, luxury apartments in Bellevue WA.', 'Clean, European styling, contemporary design and the kind of amenities typically found in the buildings across the water.', 'A home at Hyde Square puts you in the middle of what really matters in the Seattle area.', 'Features:', 'Full size, front-loading, stacked washers and dryers, Designer kitchen and bath plumbing fixtures, Stainless steel appliances, Tile tub surrounds, Modern, soft-close cabinetry, Solid-surface quartz countertops, Vaulted ceilings in all apartment homes, Wood/vinyl flooring throughout living areas, Available in most units, Private deck, patio or balcony, Tiled full-height kitchen backsplash', 'Community Amenities:', 'State-of-the-art fitness center, Luxurious landscaped courtyards, Pet spa and grooming area, Barbeque and fire pit areas, Wellness center with indoor sauna, Tavern-style bar room, Clubhouse & gourmet kitchen, Convenient package management, Business hub, Coffee lounge, Spin & yoga studio, Expansive private spa deck, Two sky lounges with rooftop access, Concierge services', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'DeAdom1S1P']
